@startuml
title Adapter

skinparam legendBackgroundColor #f9f9f9
skinparam legendBorderColor #999999

legend right
**Intent**: Convert the interface of a class into another interface clients expect.

**Use when**: Integrating incompatible interfaces, legacy code.

**Key participants**: Target, Adapter, Adaptee, Client.
endlegend

interface Target {
  +request()
}

class Adapter implements Target {
  -adaptee : Adaptee
  +request()
}

class Adaptee {
  +specificRequest()
}

class Client
Client ..> Target
Adapter o-- Adaptee
@enduml